Gan '''Ayt Nḍir''' yat tqbilt tamaziɣt illan ɣ [[Aṭlas anammas|watlas anammas]].

Kkan-tt-inn Ayt Nḍir gan ɣ teqbilin skarnin azemmal/lgic n Ayt Idila. Zzawit n Idila ad yadelli inebḍen Aṭlas Anammas ɣ tasut ᵗˢ17, qbel ad fell-as ikk ugellid aɛelwi Mulay Racid.

Ar ttinin mas d-kkan Ayt Nḍir igʷmmaḍen/ibenkan (rives) n [[Asif n Gigu|wasif n Gigu]] ɣ Waṭlas Anammas da nn-itteffin ɣ [[Asif n Sbu|wasif n Sbu]]. Ɣinn a'ɣ bnan sin iɣerman ; Alil d Talilt.

== Amutty nns ==
Gan Ayt Nḍir ɣ Ayt Idrasen. Wid kkan-tt-inn ɣ tasut ᵗˢ11 gan yan ufus ɣ Imsufen, nna igan iẓnagen zdeɣnin ɣ [[Tanezruft tutrimt|tnezruft tutrimt]]. Ɣ uzemz n [[imrabḍen]], mmatteyn Ayt Idrasen s ugafa ugmiḍ, s tesga n Tfilalt.

